"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-02-27-paris-2024-olympics-we-believe-in-god-super-falcons-abiodun-on-juju-drama-by-cameroon\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Super Falcons midfielder Deborah Abiodun has said the juju drama which unfolded in their match against Cameroon on Monday evening at the Moshood Abiola National Stadium was a mere distraction by their opponent.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 44, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deborah\", \"score\": 0.7581316978889242, \"rank\": 0.3190320399269414, \"text\": \"Deborah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deborah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deborah\"}, {\"begin\": 122, \"end\": 130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7229311393378491, \"rank\": 0.37386256458970674, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 171, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_National_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9976978165164725, \"rank\": 0.002307495762155097, \"text\": \"National Stadium\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_National_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_National_Stadium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Abiodun, the Super Falcons believe in God.\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recall that the Super Falcons piped Cameroon's Lionesses 1-0 in a crucial second leg Women's Olympic football qualifier, after a pulsating encounter in Abuja.\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 324, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7229311393378491, \"rank\": 0.37386256458970674, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9045453855238438e-28, \"text\": \"Abuja\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a little drama which unfolded at the start of the second half.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was after a Cameroonian player attempted to plant a juju-like material at the Super Falcons' goal post.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a move probably targeted at Nigeria's goalkeeper Chiamaka Nnadozie who had kept the Cameroonians at bay in Douala and Abuja.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.842210054029745, \"rank\": 0.12627288025063763, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiamaka_Nnadozie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chiamaka Nnadozie\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiamaka_Nnadozie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiamaka_Nnadozie\"}, {\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douala\", \"score\": 0.9999999886124443, \"rank\": 6.020128920210226e-09, \"text\": \"Douala\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Douala\"}, {\"begin\": 757, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9045453855238438e-28, \"text\": \"Abuja\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abuja\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The attempt was however checked and possibly the efficacy of the charm was diluted as Nnadozie prevented the Lionesses from breaching her goal.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on the development after the game, Abiodun told newsmen during a post-match conference that the move by the visitors was a tactic deployed to distract the Falcons.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We kind of saw it as a point of distraction in the game and were able to keep our focus high, regardless of whatever they believe in,\\\" the 20-year-old said.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe in God and in God we stand and put our trust.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With God all things are possible.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, we do not care about the voodoo [juju],\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2024 Olympic Qualifier: South Africa boss Ellis sets sight on Super Falcons clash  Zaidu Sanusi undergoes successful surgery in Portugal  Eid-el-Fitr: Gov Abiodun urges Muslims to sustain Ramadan deeds beyond fasting period  Let faith inspire compassion, service -  Abiodun urges Muslims at Iftar  2026 WAFCON: 'It would not happen for other tournaments' - Super Falcons' Plumptre slams CAF  WAFCON 2026: Super Falcons Ajibade disappointed with postponement  WAFCON 2026: Super Falcons decamped after postponement  Abiodun commissions phase II of Imashayi-Igan-Okoto-Ayetoro Road, pledges completion of final phase  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1418, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.7503439135323862, \"rank\": 0.33272021842499927, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Falcons\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\"